<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA63">
<l>tāḻcaṭaiyu nīṇmuṭiyu moṇmaḻuvuñ cakkaramuñ</l>
<l>cūḻaravum poṉṉāṇun tōṉṟumāṟ – cūḻun</l>
<l>tiraṇṭaruvi pāyun tirumalaimē lentaik</l>
<l>kiraṇṭuruvu moṉṟā yicaintu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Hanging matted hair and tall crown, bright axe and discus,</l>
<l>coiling snakes and gold string  appear indeed on the holy mountain</l>
<l>where all around waterfalls gather [and] spread,</l> 
<l>two forms for our Father, having joined as one.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
